  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Assessing Current Project Status**\n\nI\'m currently focused on evaluating the application\'s present state to provide a clear summary. My analysis highlights existing features to directly address the user\'s inquiry, aiming for a concise overview of the project\'s current status.\n\n\n**Analyzing Component Structure**\n\nNow I\'m diving deeper into the component structure. I\'ve re-examined the file tree, focusing on the components and associated services to grasp the application\'s modularity. The goal is to identify core features and understand their implementation without code modifications. I\'m focusing on key components and services to determine the application\'s key modules.\n\n\n**Exploring AI Game Mechanics**\n\nI\'m now integrating AI game mechanics. I\'m focusing on the AI Engine, using services/aiService.ts, /game/engine.ts, and services/geminiService.ts. I\'m dynamically generating the game world with gemini-3.1-pro-preview based on character classes and setting up linked rooms with puzzles and items. I\'m refining the player action processing, incorporating both a Narrator and an Imp persona, and implementing a hint system. Finally, I\'m working on customized scenery illustrations with gemini-2.5-flash-image for a cinematic style.\n\n\n**Generating Ambient Atmosphere**\n\nI\'m now generating ambient atmosphere. I\'m dynamically analyzing room descriptions to create Pixabay search keywords. I\'m focusing on retrieving suitable ambient background music loops and sounds for a more immersive experience.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "We are sitting in a **fully cohesive, polished, and robust text-based RPG engine** called **Gemini Realms**! The application combines rich AI-driven storytelling, dynamic asset generation, and highly immersive audio integrations in a dark, atmospheric RPG layout.\n\nHere is a breakdown of the current state of the application:\n\n### 1. \360\237\216\255 Dual-Persona Game Master (AI Engine)\nThe game is powered by a sophisticated interaction with **Gemini (`gemini-3.1-pro-preview`)**, utilizing strict JSON schema validation to drive the game\'s mechanics:\n*   **The Narrator**: An engaging, objective storyteller that guides you through details in the second-person.\n*   **The Imp**: A sarcastic, wisecracking internal companion inspired by Gilbert Gottfried\342\200\231s Iago, throwing in witty and under-15-word commentary on your actions.\n*   **Intelligent Logic**: The engine manages full turn processing, handles item tracking, awards XP, guides level-ups, evaluates combat statistics based on equipped gear, and auto-generates subtle, in-character hints if you get stuck for more than 5 turns.\n\n### 2. \360\237\214\215 Procedurally Generated Start\nUpon starting a new game and selecting a class (**Warrior, Mage, or Rogue**):\n*   A unique starting area consisting of 3\342\200\2235 interconnected rooms is dynamically created around a central theme (e.g., an ancient crypt, a decaying wizard\'s tower).\n*   **Puzzles & Obstacles**: The world-generator ensures there is always an environmental challenge (like a locked door requiring a key, or obstacles demanding specific items) in place.\n*   **Discovered Mapping**: As you travel, the game maps your location so you can pop open an interactive, visual Map overlay to track where you\'ve been.\n\n### 3. \360\237\226\274\357\270\217 Cinematic Visuals & Aesthetic UI\nThe layout is tailored strictly to an old-school, premium fantasy tabletop vibe:\n*   **Visual Stage**: Features a wide-aspect cinematic scene display on the left. The scene is dynamically illustrated based on your current room using **Gemini-2.5-Flash-Image**, enhanced with a subtle, looping **Ken-Burns animation effect** for depth.\n*   **Bespoke Typography**: Employs elegant serif display pairing (*IM Fell English*) for the narrator, coupled with an active cursive font (*Indie Flower*) to denote the Imp\'s vocal banter.\n*   **Interactive Panels**: The right-hand dashboard tracks your custom stats (HP bar, Level, XP track), features active paper-doll equipment slots, and displays a clean, grid-based inventory from which you can equip weapons/armor or consume potions with a click.\n\n### 4. \360\237\224\212 Immersive Audio Integration\n*   **Dynamic Soundscapes (Pixabay)**: Every time you step into a new room, the AI evaluates the sensory mood and drafts discrete sound-design search queries. It uses them to pull and stream matching ambient loop soundscapes from Pixabay. \n*   **Active Voice Narration (ElevenLabs)**: Implements separate ElevenLabs voices for narration, system messages, and the Imp companion, queueing up audio buffers seamlessly to keep voice passages from overlapping.\n*   **Settings Drawer**: Features a fully control-backed settings console to toggle narration, configure Pixabay or ElevenLabs API keys, test and register custom ElevenLabs voice IDs, and slide ambient volume.\n\n### 5. \360\237\233\241\357\270\217 Deep Stability & Robustness Upgrades\nIn our last session, we added a series of structural fortifications to the runtime:\n*   **JSON Bulletproofing**: Added a recursive parser and repair wrapper (`cleanAndParseJson`) that strips out accidental markdown tags and manually closes cut-off brackets/quotes to gracefully survive minor LLM formatting hiccups.\n*   **Navigation Guardrails**: The game engine validates every movement suggestion the AI makes. If the model hallucinates a path to an undefined destination, the system quietly cancels the navigation state rather than crashing your session.\n*   **Connection and Save Backups**: The game\'s robust state management tracks and saves local sessions seamlessly. Chat contexts recover automatically on page refreshes or game loads without running into uninitialized state errors."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 6
      nanos: 950657822
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
